.SKIP 1
.INDENT 5
^IF YOU HAVE INPUT A NAME THAT IS INVALID ON THE SYSTEM (EG. MISSPELLING
THE NAME) YOU WILL RECEIVE THE FOLLOWING <GFD ERROR
MESSAGE:
